data.description: Great priced 2 bedroom, 2 bath condo unit on low floor in beautiful Reflections Condominium. This unit is on the second floor and very private with views of the St. Andrews Bay. When you enter in, it has an open floor plan with beautiful upgraded hardwood floors, granite countertops, crown molding and newer stainless appliances. This unit has a great private balcony that is screened in to enjoy the Florida breeze. The unit has a split floorplan with master bedroom that has sliders to the back balcony. The master bathroom has a large walk in shower and dual sinks with granite vanities. The AC unit  and water heater were replaced in 2019 and in great working order. Reflections has all of the amenities including large resort style pool with hot tub, BBQ station, firepit, fitness center, Serenity Spa. Reflections is close to shopping, entertainment, and great restaurants.
